c: 10
v: 83
t: "fma aman lmwsa ealayh alslam mae maa 'atahum bih min alhujaj waladlt 'iilaa dhuriyat min qawmih min bani 'israyyl, wahum khayfwn min fireawn wamalayih 'ana yftnwhm baledhab, fysdduhm ean dynhm, wa'iina fireawn lajbar mstkbr fi alard, wa'iinah lamin almtjawzyn alhadi fi alkufr walfsad"